        /// wrapping around at the boundary of the type.
        ///
        /// # Examples
        ///
        /// Basic usage:
        ///
        /// ```
        #[doc = concat!("assert_eq!(3", stringify!($SelfT), ".wrapping_pow(5), 243);")]
        /// assert_eq!(3u8.wrapping_pow(6), 217);
        /// ```
