        ///
        /// This function is equivalent to `self % rhs == 0`, except that it will not panic
        /// for `rhs == 0`. Instead, `0.is_multiple_of(0) == true`, and for any non-zero `n`,
        /// `n.is_multiple_of(0) == false`.
