        /// native byte order.
        ///
        /// As the target platform's native endianness is used, portable code
        /// should use [`to_be_bytes`] or [`to_le_bytes`], as appropriate,
        /// instead.
        ///
        #[doc = $to_xe_bytes_doc]
        ///
        /// [`to_be_bytes`]: Self::to_be_bytes
        /// [`to_le_bytes`]: Self::to_le_bytes
        ///
        /// # Examples
        ///
        /// ```
